</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Maximum for item upload</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter the maximum amount of items that you want to upload to Shopgate.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item description</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select a free text field. The saved text in this field is displayed as the item description.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Add technical data to the item description</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Yes</strong> = Transfers the technical data saved in an item’s <strong>texts</strong> tab to Shopgate.<br></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>No</strong> = Technical data is not transferred.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Transfer stock unit</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select whether the <strong>position</strong> saved in a variation’s <strong>category</strong> tab should be transferred to Shopgate. The position number is used to sort items within the item listing in the plentyShop.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
