<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the cross-selling function to offer further items that match your items.<br></p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Yes</strong> = If you select <strong>Yes</strong>, a maximum of 15 cross-selling items with a maximum of 3 variations each is transferred for each item.<br></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>No</strong> = Cross-selling items will not be transferred.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
