<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter the Alias that you have received from Shopgate.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Cname</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>You can save a personal domain with your provider. In order to use this domain, it also has to be saved on Shopgate.<br>
The target <strong>cname.shopgate.com</strong> also has to be saved with the provider.</p>
</div></div></td>
